                                        <h2 class="art-postheader"><a href="./node/1178.html" title="MWL denounces demolishing mosques in Angola">MWL denounces demolishing mosques in Angola</a></h2>
                                    </div>
                                                
                <div class="art-postcontent art-postcontent-0 clearfix"><div class="art-article">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p><strong>Makkah, Muharram 26, 1435, Nov 29, 2013, SPA -- The Makkah-based Muslim World league has denounced on behalf of Muslims in the world the reported demolishing of a number of mosques and preventing Muslims from worshipping in mosques in Angola.<br />In a statement, the Secretary General of the organization, Sheikh Dr. Abdullah bin Abdulmohsen Al-Turki said the MWL has been informed of restriction measures taken and prevention of building more mosques as well as demolishing a number of them in Angola.</strong></p></div></div></div>  </div>
</div>
