                                <div class="art-postmetadataheader">
                                        <h2 class="art-postheader"><a href="./node/1174.html" title="Muslim World League and New Zealand Sign MoU on Halal Slaughter">Muslim World League and New Zealand Sign MoU on Halal Slaughter</a></h2>
                                    </div>
                                                
                <div class="art-postcontent art-postcontent-0 clearfix"><div class="art-article">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p><strong>Wellington, Muharram 25, 1435, Nov 28, 2013, SPA -- The Secretary General of Muslim World League (MWL) Dr. Abdullah bin Abdulmohsen Al-Turki signed here today a memorandum of understanding about Halal slaughter with New Zealand's Minister for Primary Industries Nathan Guy.<br />
This memorandum came as a prelude to signing an agreement in the coming period between the Muslim World League and the Government of New Zealand in relation to Halal slaughter.<br />
--SPA</strong></p></div></div></div>  </div>
</div>
