	<article class="art-post art-article">
                                <div class="art-postmetadataheader">
                                        <h2 class="art-postheader"><a href="./node/1095.html" title="Misconception about Islam needs to be removed, says MWL">Misconception about Islam needs to be removed, says MWL</a></h2>
                                    </div>
                                                
                <div class="art-postcontent art-postcontent-0 clearfix"><div class="art-article">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>LONDON: FOUZIA KHAN<br />
Published — Saturday 17 August 2013<br />
ARABNEWS</p>
<p><strong>The London branch of the Muslim World League on Thursday organized a seminar on the role of Islamic centers in correcting misconceptions about Islam at the Islamic Cultural Center.</strong></p>
<p>The seminar was organized with the aim of clarifying the role of Islamic centers in spreading awareness about Islam and Muslims and removing misconceptions.</p></div></div></div>  </div>
</div>
                                <div class="art-postmetadatafooter">
